<emphasis box="[189,450,975,1001]" italics="true" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Chaleponcus limbatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Attems C. G." box="[456,615,975,1001]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" pagination="1 - 233" refId="ref46256" refString="Attems C. G. 1914. Afrikanische Spirostreptiden nebst Uberblick uber die Spirostreptiden orbis terrarum. Zoologica Stuttgart 65 - 66: 1 - 233." type="journal article" year="1914">Attems, 1914</bibRefCitation>
